(vi) a virtual asset;
osmium, palladium, rhodium or ruthenium, in a manufactured or unmanufactured state;
precious metals and stones business (貴金屬及寶石業務) means
the business of dealing in precious metals and stones;
precious product (貴重產品) means any jewellery or watch made
up of, containing or having attached to it, any precious metal or precious stone, or both;
precious stone (寶石) means diamond, sapphire, ruby, emerald,
jade or pearl, whether natural or otherwise;
register (註冊紀錄冊), when used as a noun, means the register
maintained under section 53ZUC;
register (註冊), when used as a verb, means enter in the register
